<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 16:08:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列海法将医院移至地下，等待冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-haifa-moves-hospital-underground-waiting-for-conflict/articleshow/104379009.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104379009.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列海法的医务人员准备建造他们声称的世界上最大的地下医院，以应对冲突蔓延到该市的情况。随着该地区紧张局势升级，以色列军队一直在轰炸加沙地带，以消灭哈马斯武装分子，而黎巴嫩和叙利亚则发射火箭弹，指责以色列军队对其机场发动导弹袭击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 15:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-haifa-moves-hospital-underground-waiting-for-conflict/articleshow/104379009.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普：“你知道，真主党非常聪明”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-you-know-hezbollah-is-very-smart/articleshow/104378644.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104378644.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普在佛罗里达州的一次集会上赞扬了真主党的智慧。他还批评以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对最近哈马斯袭击事件的反应。特朗普表达了对以色列的支持，但透露以色列选择不参加消灭卡西姆·苏莱马尼将军的行动。他谴责内塔尼亚胡的决定，并指责他将任务的成功归功于他。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 15:13:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-you-know-hezbollah-is-very-smart/articleshow/104378644.cms</guid></item><item><title>乔治·索罗斯关闭了价值 250 亿美元的慈善帝国的办事处</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/george-soros-open-society-foundations-job-cuts-soros-philanthropy-empire/articleshow/104377148.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104377148.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔治·索罗斯 (George Soros) 创立的开放社会基金会 (Open Society Foundations) 正在关闭全球办事处，并裁员 40% 以上。关闭的办事处包括非洲、巴塞罗那和巴尔的摩。减少员工和办公地点的决定是出于提高运营效率的需要。该慈善机构目前每年发放超过 10 亿美元的赠款，其中超过 1 亿美元流向非洲。乔治·索罗斯的儿子亚历克斯·索罗斯现在担任该组织的主席。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 14:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/george-soros-open-society-foundations-job-cuts-soros-philanthropy-empire/articleshow/104377148.cms</guid></item><item><title>100年前沉没的一战时期船只在苏必利尔湖底部被发现</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/world-war-i-era-ship-that-sank-100-years-ago-found-at-the-bottom-of-lake-superior/articleshow/104376623.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104376623.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五大湖沉船历史协会发现了休伦顿号的残骸，这是一艘1923年被另一艘船撞到苏必利尔湖后沉没的钢铁散装货轮。这次碰撞导致两艘船暂时融合，休伦顿号的船员得以幸免于难。以安全转移。使用声纳技术在约 800 英尺的深度发现了残骸。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 13:46:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/world-war-i-era-ship-that-sank-100-years-ago-found-at-the-bottom-of-lake-superior/articleshow/104376623.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度空军待命，从以色列带回印度人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/indian-air-force-on-standby-to-bring-back-indians-from-israel/articleshow/104376373.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104376373.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度空军已准备好飞机，以应对在与哈马斯的冲突中可能从以色列撤离印度公民的情况。该机队包括 C-17 和 IL-76 等运输机以及 C-130J 超级大力士。这项行动被称为“阿贾伊行动”，旨在从以色列带回约 18,000 名印度人。印度驻以色列大使馆正在向印度公民提供援助，预计将有一架包机将230名乘客带回印度。以色列死亡人数已上升至1300人，数百人受伤，150人被哈马斯绑架。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 13:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/indian-air-force-on-standby-to-bring-back-indians-from-israel/articleshow/104376373.cms</guid></item><item><title>从安全威胁到现金短缺：中巴走廊是否遇到重大障碍？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/from-security-threats-to-cash-crunch-has-china-pakistan-corridor-hit-a-major-roadblock/articleshow/104376258.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104376258.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国对中巴经济走廊（CPEC）的资助放缓，导致该项目陷入僵局。经济和安全因素，包括中国自身的经济放缓和巴基斯坦的安全威胁，是造成这种放缓的原因。俾路支叛乱分子和巴基斯坦塔利班对中国工人的袭击使基建项目的进展进一步复杂化。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 13:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/from-security-threats-to-cash-crunch-has-china-pakistan-corridor-hit-a-major-roadblock/articleshow/104376258.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国称没有直接证据表明伊朗与哈马斯对以色列的袭击有关</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/no-direct-evidence-tying-iran-to-hamas-attacks-on-israel-france-says/articleshow/104376118.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104376118.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国外交部周四表示，没有任何正式证据表明伊朗参与了哈马斯对以色列的袭击，并补充说巴黎已向地区行为者传递信息，警告不要利用这场危机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 13:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/no-direct-evidence-tying-iran-to-hamas-attacks-on-israel-france-says/articleshow/104376118.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊姆兰·汗：在任何情况下都不会离开巴基斯坦</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/will-not-leave-pakistan-under-any-circumstances-imran-khan/articleshow/104375640.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104375640.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;目前正在监狱服刑的巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗宣布，他不会离开这个国家，并将继续为自由和法治而奋斗。汗于八月因涉嫌违反《官方保密法》而被捕，他表示，他现在比以往任何时候都更强大。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 12:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/will-not-leave-pakistan-under-any-circumstances-imran-khan/articleshow/104375640.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙开发后新加坡加强安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-steps-up-security-following-gaza-development/articleshow/104374836.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104374836.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;内政和法律部长尚穆根表示，新加坡根据加沙局势加强了警察巡逻，并重新评估了潜在目标袭击地点的安全。安全机构正在密切监视局势，并已采取措施加强高风险地区的安全部署。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 12:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-steps-up-security-following-gaza-development/articleshow/104374836.cms</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚国家电视台称以色列袭击目标阿勒颇和大马士革机场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/syria-state-tv-says-israeli-attack-targets-aleppo-damascus-airports/articleshow/104374151.cms</link><description>叙利亚国家电视台称，以色列对首都大马士革和北部城市阿勒颇的主要机场发动了袭击。当地媒体频道 Sham FM 称，叙利亚针对这两起袭击启动了防空系统。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 11:58:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/syria-state-tv-says-israeli-attack-targets-aleppo-damascus-airports/articleshow/104374151.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃森哲称美国司法部正在调查其为政府提供的服务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accenture-says-us-justice-department-probing-its-services-to-government/articleshow/104373859.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104373859.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃森哲证实，美国司法部正在调查其子公司埃森哲联邦服务公司，此前有指控称，埃森哲的一名或多名员工向政府提供了有关该公司遵守联邦安全控制措施的不准确信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 11:51:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/accenture-says-us-justice-department-probing-its-services-to-government/articleshow/104373859.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我非常关心......”：以色列士兵在被哈马斯杀害前给家人发短信</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/i-deeply-care-israeli-solider-texts-family-moment-before-being-killed-by-hamas/articleshow/104373853.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104373853.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名 19 岁的以色列士兵纳马·博尼 (Naama Boni) 下士在一场致命战斗中被哈马斯恐怖分子杀害前不久给家人发短信。她对附近的恐怖分子表示担忧，并提到头部受伤。博尼还录制了一段声音颤抖的视频。她的姨妈希姆里特·伊卢克 (Shimrit Ilook) 谈到了她侄女的去世以及一周前他们如何庆祝她的生日。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 11:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/i-deeply-care-israeli-solider-texts-family-moment-before-being-killed-by-hamas/articleshow/104373853.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯杜马将于下周就废除核试验条约的批准进行投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russian-duma-to-vote-next-week-on-scrapping-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty/articleshow/104372942.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104372942.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯议会国家杜马将投票决定撤销莫斯科对禁止核试验全球条约的批准。此举预计将获得一致批准，可能为俄罗斯自 1990 年以来首次进行核试验提供法律保障。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 11:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russian-duma-to-vote-next-week-on-scrapping-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty/articleshow/104372942.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在以色列告诉内塔尼亚胡：美国不会去任何地方</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-tells-netanyahu-in-israel-us-not-going-anywhere/articleshow/104372374.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104372374.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务卿布林肯访问以色列表示支持并阻止与哈马斯的冲突蔓延。他的目标是确保人质获释，推进加沙平民安全通行谈判，并向伊朗发出威慑信息。布林肯向以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡保证，美国致力于继续参与其中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 11:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-tells-netanyahu-in-israel-us-not-going-anywhere/articleshow/104372374.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯再次袭击乌克兰南部后，北约成员国罗马尼亚在其土壤上发现更多无人机碎片</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-member-romania-finds-more-drone-fragments-on-its-soil-after-russian-again-hits-southern-ukraine/articleshow/104371586.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104371586.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在罗马尼亚与乌克兰边境附近发现了一架疑似因撞击而爆炸的无人机，引发了人们对俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争蔓延到北约成员国的担忧。罗马尼亚当局检测到一系列无人机前往乌克兰河港，罗马尼亚境内发现的无人机碎片已被证实与俄罗斯军队使用的无人机碎片相似。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-member-romania-finds-more-drone-fragments-on-its-soil-after-russian-again-hits-southern-ukraine/articleshow/104371586.cms</guid></item><item><title>外交部称中国没有脱北者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-north-korean-defectors-in-china-foreign-ministry-says/articleshow/104371615.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104371615.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国外交部否认了有关中国本周驱逐了约 600 名脱北者的报道。发言人表示，中方不存在“所谓脱北者”，中方依法处理非法入境朝鲜人员问题。韩国外交部表示正在努力核实这些报道，并将继续采取外交努力保护脱北者。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:54:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-north-korean-defectors-in-china-foreign-ministry-says/articleshow/104371615.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本公司将发行数字货币用于清洁能源交易</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/japan-firms-to-issue-digital-currency-for-clean-energy-transaction/articleshow/104370690.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104370690.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加密货币交易所 DeCurret 周四表示，一群日本公司将在 2024 年 7 月之前发行一种数字货币，用于清洁能源证书的交易和结算。 GMO Aozora Net Bank 将发行基于日元的数字货币，称为“DCJPY”，该货币将在 DeCurret 推出的网络上运行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:31:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/japan-firms-to-issue-digital-currency-for-clean-energy-transaction/articleshow/104370690.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击：组织以色列狂欢派对的双胞胎发生了什么</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-attack-what-happened-to-twins-who-organized-israel-rave-party/articleshow/104371044.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104371044.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以在以色列组织狂欢派对而闻名的双胞胎兄弟在一次活动中遭到哈马斯袭击，导致一人死亡、另一人失踪，从而面临悲剧。家人悲痛万分，同时希望失踪的兄弟能够平安归来。双胞胎的快乐精神和为他人带来幸福的热情在悲伤中被铭记。与此同时，以色列宣布将维持对加沙地带的封锁，直至所有人质获释。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-attack-what-happened-to-twins-who-organized-israel-rave-party/articleshow/104371044.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着选举临近，波兰总理警告移民中存在“伊斯兰战士”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/as-election-nears-polish-pm-warns-of-islamic-fighters-among-migrants/articleshow/104370011.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104370011.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰总理马特乌什·莫拉维茨基声称，由于以色列冲突，伊斯兰武装分子将成为前往欧洲的移民之一。民族主义法律与正义党（PiS）反对欧盟重新安置移民的配额制度，并在竞选活动中使用反移民言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 10:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/as-election-nears-polish-pm-warns-of-islamic-fighters-among-migrants/articleshow/104370011.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚希望联合国法院采取旨在保护纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫亚美尼亚人权利的措施</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenia-wants-a-un-court-to-impose-measures-aimed-at-protecting-rights-of-nagorno-karabakh-armenians/articleshow/104369527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104369527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚美尼亚周四敦促联合国最高法院对阿塞拜疆实施新的临时命令，以防止亚美尼亚法律小组领导人所说的阿塞拜疆对纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地区的“种族清洗”变得不可逆转。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 09:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenia-wants-a-un-court-to-impose-measures-aimed-at-protecting-rights-of-nagorno-karabakh-armenians/articleshow/104369527.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>